},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
"Don't Be Tricked"
]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"93c53a",
"children":[
"Do not order vaginal cultures to diagnose the cause of vaginitis."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"ec2cf0",
"children":[
"Treatment of vulvovaginal candidiasis can be initiated empirically if symptoms are accompanied by characteristic findings."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
